Mantle,is,a,D,rendering,graphics,API,that,allows,PC,games,utilizing,the,Graphics,Core,Next,GPU,architecture,to,reduce,CPU,overhead,Mantle,frees,up,processing,space,for,more,complex,applications,to,run,more,efficiently,without,latency,This,is,done,through,pre,building,and,re,using,data,results,and,allowing,applications,to,directly,manage,their,GPU,in,various,environments